com.JasonILTG.ScienceMod

Interface IScienceNBT

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompoundSubstance, ElementSubstance, HeatManager, HeatSinkManager, HeatVentManager, Manager, PowerManager, SubstanceBase, TEAcceleratorController.AcceleratorManager, TileHeatManager, TilePowerManager

    public interface IScienceNBT
    Classes that implement this interface must ensure that executing readFromDataTag(makeDataTag()) will not alter the essential states of the object.
    Author:
    JasonILTG and syy1125

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound makeDataTag()
      Generates a data tag for the manager.
      void readFromDataTag(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound dataTag)
      Reads the information from the data tag.

    • Method Detail

      • makeDataTag

        net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound makeDataTag()
        Generates a data tag for the manager. It is recommended that subclasses of a superclass that implements this method call the super method and append onto the generated tag to maximize the amount of information stored.
        Returns:
        The tag containing information about the manager

      • readFromDataTag

        void readFromDataTag(net.minecraft.nbt.NBTTagCompound dataTag)
        Reads the information from the data tag. It is recommended that subclasses of a superclass that implements this method call the super method at the beginning of the execution to ensure complete retrieval of data.
        Parameters:
        dataTag - The tag that contains the information about this manager.
